# Environment Variables for Vercel Deployment

## Copy these to Vercel Dashboard → Settings → Environment Variables

VITE_API_URL=
VITE_FIREBASE_API_KEY=
VITE_FIREBASE_AUTH_DOMAIN=
VITE_FIREBASE_PROJECT_ID=
VITE_FIREBASE_STORAGE_BUCKET=
VITE_FIREBASE_MESSAGING_SENDER_ID=
VITE_FIREBASE_APP_ID=

## Instructions:
## 1. Get your backend API URL from your deployed backend (e.g., https://bookcourier-server.vercel.app/api)
## 2. Get Firebase credentials from Firebase Console → Project Settings → General
## 3. Add each variable individually in Vercel dashboard
## 4. Format: VARIABLE_NAME = value (no quotes needed in Vercel)
